author: James Delingpole
title: Doubts Cast on Story About ‘Britain’s Youngest Coronavirus Victim’
description: A 21-year-old woman with no pre-existing health conditions reported as having died from coronavirus may not have had it after all.
content:
A 21-year-old woman who was reported as having died from coronavirus may not have had it after all.
